  "title": "Warehouse Operation Executive [Pasir Panjang | 5 days | up to $2600] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Warehouse Operative </strong></h3><p><strong>5 days, 9am-6pm </strong></p><p><strong>Salary: up to $2600</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Boon Leat Terrace, Singapore 119844 (Pasir Panjang)</strong></p><p><u><strong>Job scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Verify accuracy of incoming and outgoing shipments and orders. Compare identifying information with bills of lading, invoices, orders, or other records to verify that materials received are as ordered.</li><li>Maintain accurate computerized records of all material transactions.</li><li>Perform physical and/or administrative tasks involved in the shipping, storing, and distribution of materials, supplies, and equipment.</li><li>Prepare and maintain records of merchandise shipped, post weights and shipping charges, and prepare goods for final shipment.</li><li>Set up daily pickups via UPS, FedEx, DHL, and other carriers.</li><li>Load delivery trucks with order packages for delivery routes.</li><li>Lift weights up to 22kg</li><li>Follow safety standards stringently when handling products weighing more than 22kg</li><li>Use carts, dollies, hand trucks, and other gear to move heavy items around.</li><li>Perform all work in accordance with quality standards and established procedures.</li><li>Engage in cross-functional communication and interaction with various departments, including Regulatory, Customer Service, Supply Chain, etc.</li><li>Process returns in a timely manner, following provided procedures to complete tasks.</li><li>Complete warehousing and inventory execution tasks as applicable.</li><li>Assist in other areas and perform additional duties as needed.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>With warehouse experience and basic computer skills</li><li>Experience in SAP Business One </li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
